project_info.name: The Semantic Detective
project_info.description: AI-powered semantic search system for customer support tickets using BigQuery ML

semantic_search.description: Two methods of semantic search: manual cosine similarity and vector index search

gemini_rag.description: Retrieval-Augmented Generation system with query embedding, similar ticket retrieval, and AI response generation

new_ticket_flow.description: New ticket processing with dual response generation (RAG vs Pure AI)

missing_resolutions.description: AI-powered resolution generation for tickets with missing resolutions

vector_index.description: Vector index configuration and status information

embeddings_sample.description: Sample embeddings data for verification and analysis

technical_highlights: Complete semantic search implementation with two methods
Advanced RAG system using BigQuery ML and Gemini
Dual response generation showing data quality impact
AI-powered resolution generation for missing data
Professional vector indexing for scalable search
data_quality_insights: Demonstrates impact of poor data quality on AI responses
Shows comparison between RAG and pure AI approaches
Highlights importance of data quality in AI systems
Provides practical solutions for working with imperfect data
